# Read only in dev builds (`cargo run --example probe` and the in-app "Dev sign-in"
# fallback, since custom-scheme deep links can't round-trip under `tauri dev` on
# macOS). A released build never reads these — it obtains its token via the
# deep-link sign-in against SPOTLIGHT_AUTH_URL.
